\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces  Forward predictions of 2,4-D effects on metamorphosis traits based on two alternative PMoAs. Distributions are plotted as kernel density estimates and show the distributions across individuals. Variability in model output reflects individual variability. M = increase in maintenance costs, A = decrease in assimilation efficiency. G46 = developmental stage gosner stage 46. MAPE = mean absolute percent error, calculated only for predictions. }}{12}{figure.3}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:metamorps_24D}{{3}{12}{Forward predictions of 2,4-D effects on metamorphosis traits based on two alternative PMoAs. Distributions are plotted as kernel density estimates and show the distributions across individuals. Variability in model output reflects individual variability. M = increase in maintenance costs, A = decrease in assimilation efficiency. G46 = developmental stage gosner stage 46. MAPE = mean absolute percent error, calculated only for predictions}{figure.3}{}}
