\newlabel{fig:mixture_metamorphs}{{7}{20}{Predicted effects of Flupyradifurone/Sivanto and 2,4-D on metamorphosis traits. Error bands indicate 5th to 95th percentiles. Variability in model output reflects individual variability. G46 = GS 46. FLP = Flupyradifurone}{figure.7}{}}
